public View onCreateView(LayoutInflater inflater,

Overridden method that is called when the Fragment is created.

This method prepares the Fragment for use by setting the Facebook UiLifecycleHelper, setting the content view, initializing the LoginButton, and setting permissions on the LoginButton.

Overrides:

Parameters:

savedInstanceState - If non-null, this fragment is being re-constructed from a previous saved state as given here.
Returns:
